Agendize,provides,conversion,tools,that,help,businesses,convert,web,visitors,into,leads,and,clients,and,track,everything,along,the,way,These,tools,include,Click,to,Call,Send,to,Phone,by,SMS,Live,Chat,Online,Scheduling,and,more,The,Agendize,APIs,allow,customization,of,these,tools,and,retrieval,of,all,reporting,data,The,Platform,API,lets,users,create,and,manage,Agendize,accounts,buttons,and,campaigns,from,within,their,own,application,With,the,Agendize,Platform,API,users,can,manage,several,aspects,of,their,Agendize,account,Create,modify,buttons,Create,modify,campaigns,Create,modify,user,accounts,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML